	     "Implemented by Andre Gomes.\n"
	     "Test from http://www.cse.scitech.ac.uk/ccg/dft/"
	     "data_pt_x_pw91.html\n"); 
  SET_GGA_ENERGY_FUNCTION(f,energy);
  const double d[] = 
